Because they care for me!

14
00:02:29,040 --> 00:02:30,570
Why don't you care about me?

15
00:02:46,320 --> 00:02:47,040
Aunt,

16
00:02:48,360 --> 00:02:48,760
I'm sorry

17
00:02:48,760 --> 00:02:49,400
to have let you

18
00:02:49,400 --> 00:02:50,440
see this.

19
00:02:51,960 --> 00:02:53,360
Thank you for helping us.

20
00:02:53,520 --> 00:02:55,360
You're welcome. It's what I should have done.

21
