Don't be angry with your mother.

22
00:02:59,520 --> 00:03:00,520
I'm really sorry.

23
00:03:02,680 --> 00:03:03,880
Ling Xiao!

24
00:03:08,800 --> 00:03:11,440
♫Darling♫

25
00:03:12,200 --> 00:03:15,600
♫Sometimes♫

26
00:03:15,600 --> 00:03:20,320
♫I feel really exhausted♫

27
00:03:22,320 --> 00:03:24,160
♫And I would♫

28
00:03:25,680 --> 00:03:28,960
♫shed tears♫

29
00:03:28,640 --> 00:03:29,320
I'm sorry.

30
00:03:28,960 --> 00:03:34,200
♫in loneliness♫

31
00:03:32,280 --> 00:03:34,160
It was not because of your mother.

32
00:03:35,320 --> 00:03:36,850
I don't want you to meet her.

33
00:03:39,880 --> 00:03:41,140
When you see her again,

34
00:03:42,200 --> 00:03:47,840
♫This is what growing up is like♫

35
00:03:42,880 --> 00:03:44,810
stay as far away from her as you can.

36
00:03:48,640 --> 00:03:49,320
I think

37
00:03:49,320 --> 00:03:51,040
she'll hate me more then.

38
00:03:52,480 --> 00:03:54,560
I planned to be on my best behavior.

39
00:03:55,480 --> 00:04:01,840
♫We used to rely on each other♫

40
00:03:55,680 --> 00:03:57,480
After all, I'm her junior.

41
00:04:02,200 --> 00:04:04,160
♫bearing the burden♫

42
00:04:03,280 --> 00:04:04,920
If she wants to be respected,

43
00:04:05,720 --> 00:04:07,680
she should at least be respectable.

44
00:04:05,800 --> 00:04:08,560
♫and suffering the loss♫

45
00:04:08,800 --> 00:04:14,200
♫but we still look forward to the future♫

46
00:04:12,000 --> 00:04:13,520
We can't do that.

47
00:04:14,840 --> 00:04:16,200
She's your mother.

48
00:04:15,680 --> 00:04:22,040
♫Maybe you are trying hard♫

49
00:04:22,280 --> 00:04:28,640
♫to forget that just as I am♫

50
00:04:35,640 --> 00:04:37,880
♫To fly♫

51
00:04:39,159 --> 00:04:40,360
Don't be sad.

52
00:04:40,800 --> 00:04:42,080
People say unpleasant things

53
00:04:42,080 --> 00:04:43,440
when they're angry.

54
00:04:45,480 --> 00:04:46,320
I know.

55
00:04:48,960 --> 00:04:49,800
But this time

56
00:04:49,880 --> 00:04:51,680
I really want to make it up to him.

57
00:04:52,560 --> 00:04:53,520
I know

58
00:04:54,400 --> 00:04:56,280
I've done many wrong things.

59
00:04:57,240 --> 00:04:58,760
When he was little,

60
00:04:58,760 --> 00:05:00,120
when he needed me most,

61
00:05:00,120 --> 00:05:02,160
I wasn't there for him,

62
00:05:03,320 --> 00:05:07,000
so I want to spend more time with him

63
00:05:07,040 --> 00:05:08,240
to help him,

64
00:05:08,520 --> 00:05:10,040
take care of him

65
00:05:10,080 --> 00:05:11,640
and be with him.

66
00:05:13,000 --> 00:05:14,480
But I didn't expect

67
00:05:17,360 --> 00:05:19,120
it to be so hard.

68
00:05:22,760 --> 00:05:24,280
Mothers in this world

69
00:05:24,600 --> 00:05:25,600
are the same.

70
00:05:26,120 --> 00:05:27,640
But even if you don't like

71
00:05:27,640 --> 00:05:28,640
his girlfriend,

72
00:05:29,320 --> 00:05:30,000
you should

73
00:05:30,000 --> 00:05:31,280
tolerate it.

74
00:05:32,080 --> 00:05:33,600
Besides they're

75
00:05:34,360 --> 00:05:35,880
so in love right now.

76
00:05:38,760 --> 00:05:39,680
I know.

77
00:05:41,080 --> 00:05:42,080
But I really don't like

78
00:05:42,080 --> 00:05:43,520
this girl.

79
00:05:44,560 --> 00:05:46,159
No wonder you don't like her.

80
00:05:46,800 --> 00:05:47,920
I don't think

81
00:05:47,960 --> 00:05:49,090
she's good, either.

82
00:05:49,200 --> 00:05:50,000
She doesn't try

83
00:05:50,000 --> 00:05:51,400
to make you happy,

84
00:05:51,960 --> 00:05:52,800
and she even

85
00:05:53,560 --> 00:05:54,800
asked Ling Xiao to...

86
00:05:57,159 --> 00:05:57,760
If they get married

87
00:05:57,760 --> 00:05:58,880
in the future,

88
00:05:59,440 --> 00:06:02,640
your son won't be yours again.

89
00:06:22,120 --> 00:06:22,760
Mom.

90
00:06:23,600 --> 00:06:24,440
Ms. Song.

91
00:06:24,680 --> 00:06:26,440
Mingyue, what brought you here?

92
00:06:26,440 --> 00:06:28,000
Your mother didn't tell me that you were coming.

93
00:06:28,000 --> 00:06:30,400
I need to see my mother for something urgent.

94
00:06:30,400 --> 00:06:32,640
Mrs. Qi, then I'll leave you to it.

95
00:06:32,640 --> 00:06:34,040
I'll go and eat by myself.

96
00:06:34,040 --> 00:06:34,440
OK.

97
00:06:34,440 --> 00:06:35,200
See you later.

98
00:06:35,200 --> 00:06:36,330
Thank you, Ms. Song.

99
00:06:39,200 --> 00:06:39,720
Mom,

100
00:06:39,960 --> 00:06:41,440
why would you

101
00:06:41,440 --> 00:06:42,640
do this with my dad?

102
00:06:42,800 --> 00:06:43,280
It will make

103
00:06:43,280 --> 00:06:43,800
your father and you happy

104
00:06:43,800 --> 00:06:44,560
if we get a divorce, right?

105
00:06:44,560 --> 00:06:45,840
Please don't be mad.

106
00:06:45,920 --> 00:06:46,600
Are you really going to get a divorce

107
00:06:46,600 --> 00:06:48,200
with my dad on Friday?

108
00:06:48,640 --> 00:06:49,920
It will make both of you happy.

109
00:06:49,920 --> 00:06:50,720
Then you can go

110
00:06:50,720 --> 00:06:51,120
wherever you want

111
00:06:51,120 --> 00:06:53,120
and you don't need to lie to me again.

112
00:06:54,400 --> 00:06:55,920
Mom, I'm sorry.

113
00:06:56,800 --> 00:06:58,400
I'm so sorry.

114
00:07:01,320 --> 00:07:03,280
When I was in high school,

115
00:07:03,280 --> 00:07:04,920
I was really childish.

116
00:07:05,800 --> 00:07:07,600
I really regret it now.

117
00:07:07,600 --> 00:07:08,960
I fought against you

118
00:07:08,960 --> 00:07:11,280
and I didn't get a good result.

119
00:07:14,960 --> 00:07:15,920
I could have been admitted

120
00:07:15,920 --> 00:07:17,840
into a better university.

121
00:07:19,880 --> 00:07:21,240
I'm sorry to have let you down.

122
00:07:21,240 --> 00:07:22,920
I'm sorry.

123
00:07:27,400 --> 00:07:29,000
You think you've let me down?

124
00:07:29,800 --> 00:07:31,600
You've let yourself down!

125
00:07:32,159 --> 00:07:33,320
Everyone works so hard

126
00:07:33,320 --> 00:07:34,120
to get into a great college.

127
00:07:34,120 --> 00:07:35,650
Do you think they're fools?

128
00:07:36,360 --> 00:07:38,640
If you could get admitted to Tsinghua or Peking University,

129
00:07:38,640 --> 00:07:39,920
do you think I would have stopped you?

130
00:07:39,920 --> 00:07:42,080
I really regret it.

131
00:07:43,720 --> 00:07:44,520
I kept it

132
00:07:44,520 --> 00:07:46,320
in my mind for so long,

133
00:07:46,320 --> 00:07:48,760
but I can't tell you about it.

134
00:07:49,080 --> 00:07:50,240
Right now,

135
00:07:50,240 --> 00:07:51,480
I just want to go back

136
00:07:51,480 --> 00:07:53,010
and slap myself in the face.

137
00:07:53,120 --> 00:07:54,640
I can slap you in the face right now.

138
00:07:54,640 --> 00:07:55,040
I...

139
00:07:58,280 --> 00:07:59,040
Mom!

140
00:07:59,800 --> 00:08:00,720
Mom!

141
00:08:01,840 --> 00:08:03,370
Please don't hit yourself.

142
00:08:07,840 --> 00:08:09,560
Please don't!

143
00:08:09,560 --> 00:08:12,280
Why do you both hate me so much?

144
00:08:12,320 --> 00:08:14,560
How could you do this to me?

145
00:08:15,760 --> 00:08:17,440
What have I done wrong?

146
00:08:17,440 --> 00:08:19,120
Tell me!

147
00:08:19,480 --> 00:08:20,840
I've spent my life

148
00:08:20,840 --> 00:08:22,800
for the two of you,

149
00:08:23,840 --> 00:08:25,520
but now you just want

150
00:08:25,520 --> 00:08:27,240
to leave me.

151
00:08:42,400 --> 00:08:43,000
Mom!

152
00:08:45,320 --> 00:08:46,680
Do you hate me and want to abandon me

153
00:08:46,680 --> 00:08:48,280
just because I want

154
00:08:49,400 --> 00:08:51,130
to work in Beijing for two years

155
00:08:52,400 --> 00:08:54,760
and I didn't listen to you?

156
00:08:57,440 --> 00:08:58,840
Don't you want to go to Beijing

157
00:08:58,840 --> 00:09:00,120
to run away from me?

158
00:09:00,120 --> 00:09:01,960
Do you think I don't know it?

159
00:09:05,840 --> 00:09:08,600
I thought so before,

160
00:09:10,160 --> 00:09:11,480
but Mom,

161
00:09:12,560 --> 00:09:14,420
right now I'm doing it for myself.

162
00:09:15,720 --> 00:09:17,160
I want to be a journalist,

163
00:09:17,160 --> 00:09:18,280
you know?

164
00:09:19,080 --> 00:09:21,040
I love this job.

165
00:09:21,560 --> 00:09:23,240
I don't want to just take phone calls

166
00:09:23,240 --> 00:09:24,280
at a local channel

167
00:09:24,280 --> 00:09:25,240
to mediate.

168
00:09:25,440 --> 00:09:26,640
I want to report current affairs.

169
00:09:26,640 --> 00:09:27,760
I want to report people's lives.

170
00:09:27,760 --> 00:09:29,920
I want to be a documentary journalist.

171
00:09:32,280 --> 00:09:34,800
Mom, that's my dream.

172
00:09:35,720 --> 00:09:36,920
Do you understand it?

173
00:09:52,600 --> 00:09:53,280
I was wondering

174
00:09:53,280 --> 00:09:55,080
why you were home during the day.

175
00:09:56,400 --> 00:09:57,840
So that senior of yours

176
00:09:57,960 --> 00:09:59,360
saw your design

177
00:10:00,040 --> 00:10:01,500
when he was at your studio?

178
00:10:04,400 --> 00:10:05,240
He came to visit me

179
00:10:05,240 --> 00:10:06,600
when he heard

180
00:10:06,600 --> 00:10:07,930
that I started a studio.

181
00:10:08,920 --> 00:10:09,960
My sketchbook

182
00:10:09,960 --> 00:10:11,280
was on my working table

183
00:10:12,000 --> 00:10:13,930
and he picked it up and looked at it.

184
00:10:15,600 --> 00:10:17,120
How would I have known it?

185
00:10:18,120 --> 00:10:19,080
You said it was based

186
00:10:19,080 --> 00:10:20,040
on a photo,

187
00:10:20,640 --> 00:10:21,500
so which photo?

188
00:10:23,000 --> 00:10:24,240
Back then,

189
00:10:24,680 --> 00:10:26,210
when we were in high school,

190
00:10:27,280 --> 00:10:28,680
Mingyue took a photo of us

191
00:10:28,840 --> 00:10:30,120
with the camera her mother bought for her

192
00:10:30,120 --> 00:10:31,850
when we were on the playground.

193
00:10:32,240 --> 00:10:32,880
Like this.

194
00:10:45,520 --> 00:10:46,580
Let's take a photo.

195
00:10:47,080 --> 00:10:48,920
Come. One, two, three.

196
00:10:51,000 --> 00:10:52,400
She gave us the photos

197
00:10:52,400 --> 00:10:53,360
later on.

198
00:10:54,760 --> 00:10:55,800
So where is it now?

199
00:10:57,640 --> 00:10:58,800
I put it

200
00:10:59,040 --> 00:11:01,440
in a time capsule

201
00:11:01,440 --> 00:11:02,400
back then.

202
00:11:03,160 --> 00:11:04,360
Where did you bury it?

203
00:11:04,680 --> 00:11:06,440
It was a vacant lot,

204
00:11:07,200 --> 00:11:08,040
but now...

205
00:11:13,560 --> 00:11:14,560
It's hopeless.

206
00:11:15,960 --> 00:11:16,840
When I was in college,

207
00:11:16,840 --> 00:11:17,840
my laptop was stolen,

208
00:11:17,840 --> 00:11:20,240
so I don't have the electronic version now.

209
00:11:20,800 --> 00:11:21,960
She developed the films

210
00:11:21,960 --> 00:11:22,960
and gave one

211
00:11:22,960 --> 00:11:24,080
to both you and Ziqiu.

212
00:11:24,080 --> 00:11:25,040
Where is yours?

213
00:11:28,120 --> 00:11:30,360
I don't know where I put it.

214
00:11:32,920 --> 00:11:34,080
Let's go to Ziqiu.

215
00:11:34,080 --> 00:11:35,720
He's good at keeping stuff.

216
00:11:36,200 --> 00:11:36,920
Right now?

217
00:11:37,560 --> 00:11:38,680
I'll get you a cup of coffee

218
00:11:38,680 --> 00:11:40,440
to cheer you up.

219
00:11:41,680 --> 00:11:42,210
Let's go.

220
00:11:45,800 --> 00:11:46,920
A glass of kiwi smoothie,

221
00:11:46,920 --> 00:11:47,640
a cup of latte

222
00:11:47,640 --> 00:11:48,640
and a fruit salad.

223
00:11:49,080 --> 00:11:50,520
There’s a fruit salad

224
00:11:50,520 --> 00:11:51,520
in our sandwich set menu,

225
00:11:51,520 --> 00:11:52,120
so would you like

226
00:11:52,120 --> 00:11:53,480
to have a salad set menu instead?

227
00:11:53,480 --> 00:11:53,920
OK.

228
00:11:53,920 --> 00:11:56,040
OK, a salad set menu.

229
00:11:56,280 --> 00:11:57,320
It's 92 yuan in total.

230
00:11:57,320 --> 00:11:58,280
Cash or WeChat pay?

231
00:11:58,280 --> 00:11:58,960
WeChat pay.

232
00:11:59,240 --> 00:12:00,440
Please scan the code.

233
00:12:01,360 --> 00:12:02,520
WeChat pay.

234
00:12:08,400 --> 00:12:09,120
Ziqiu,

235
00:12:09,120 --> 00:12:10,120
a glass of kiwi smoothie

236
00:12:10,120 --> 00:12:10,920
and a cup of latte.

237
00:12:10,920 --> 00:12:11,280
OK.

238
00:12:12,120 --> 00:12:13,640
And a sandwich set, please.

239
00:12:13,640 --> 00:12:14,160
OK!

240
00:12:14,760 --> 00:12:15,640
Welcome!

241
00:12:19,160 --> 00:12:20,420
What brought you here?

242
00:12:20,800 --> 00:12:22,400
Don't you have to work today?

243
00:12:22,480 --> 00:12:24,040
I've changed shifts with my colleague.

244
00:12:24,040 --> 00:12:25,160
It seems you're doing great.

245
00:12:25,160 --> 00:12:26,040
You do look like

246
00:12:26,280 --> 00:12:27,340
an adult right now.

247
00:12:27,720 --> 00:12:29,450
Waitresses are just like this.

248
00:12:31,240 --> 00:12:32,640
Smile when you're happy.

249
00:12:32,640 --> 00:12:34,240
No need to pretend to be cool.

250
00:12:37,160 --> 00:12:38,280
What do you want to drink?

251
00:12:38,280 --> 00:12:39,410
What are you good at?

252
00:12:39,520 --> 00:12:40,360
Fruit juice.

253
00:12:41,920 --> 00:12:43,400
OK, please give us

254
00:12:43,400 --> 00:12:45,000
two glasses of orange juice.

255
00:12:51,880 --> 00:12:53,320
Your sister is really like you.

256
00:12:53,320 --> 00:12:54,880
Sure she does.

257
00:12:56,760 --> 00:12:58,280
Cao, someone from my family are here,

258
00:12:58,280 --> 00:12:58,960
so help me make the coffee.

259
00:12:58,960 --> 00:12:59,400
OK!

260
00:12:59,640 --> 00:13:00,300
Have a seat.

261
00:13:04,440 --> 00:13:05,320
I lived in Zhao Huaguang's house

262
00:13:05,320 --> 00:13:06,760
when I first got abroad

263
00:13:08,040 --> 00:13:09,480
and I was in a hurry when I left.

264
00:13:09,480 --> 00:13:10,840
So I left many things in his place.

265
00:13:10,840 --> 00:13:12,970
I don't know if he has thrown them away.

266
00:13:16,280 --> 00:13:17,040
Ziqiu,

267
00:13:17,080 --> 00:13:17,520
you can call

268
00:13:17,520 --> 00:13:18,650
and ask him about it.

269
00:13:20,680 --> 00:13:22,080
Just go back to your work.

270
00:13:23,720 --> 00:13:24,980
Ling Xiao, look for it.

271
00:13:25,320 --> 00:13:25,840
Maybe that album

272
00:13:25,840 --> 00:13:26,400
was still in one

273
00:13:26,400 --> 00:13:26,880
of your boxes.

274
00:13:26,880 --> 00:13:27,800
When you moved over,

275
00:13:27,800 --> 00:13:29,000
you got so many boxes.

276
00:13:29,760 --> 00:13:31,020
I really can't find it.

277
00:13:33,920 --> 00:13:35,780
Sorry, but I'd like to interrupt.

278
00:13:36,160 --> 00:13:37,560
I'm not clear about my brother's other stuff,

279
00:13:37,560 --> 00:13:38,800
but I'm clear about his albums.

280
00:13:38,800 --> 00:13:39,530
Qin Meiyang!

281
00:13:40,640 --> 00:13:42,760
Three years ago,

282
00:13:44,080 --> 00:13:45,680
my mother cut those photos into pieces.

283
00:13:45,680 --> 00:13:46,840
If I hadn't noticed it

284
00:13:46,840 --> 00:13:48,320
and hidden all his certificates,

285
00:13:48,320 --> 00:13:49,000
they would have been cut

286
00:13:49,000 --> 00:13:49,930
into pieces too.

287
00:13:50,400 --> 00:13:51,520
It's in the past

288
00:13:51,520 --> 00:13:52,560
and don't mention it ever again.

289
00:13:52,560 --> 00:13:53,080
If I were you,

290
00:13:53,080 --> 00:13:54,320
I would tell them all about it

291
00:13:54,320 --> 00:13:55,160
to get them

292
00:13:55,160 --> 00:13:56,160
better prepared.

293
00:13:56,280 --> 00:13:57,280
Or when mom gets crazy,

